           X2=X2-3.-ETA2-5.*ETA2*ETA2/4.                                83 00700
           X2=ETA2*ETA2*X2/(1.-(ETA2/2.)**2)**2                         83 00710
           B2S2=1.-X1-X2                                                83 00720
           B2S2=B2S2*B2S2                                               83 00730
        ELSE                                                            83 00740
